Class IdentifierFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.factory.IdentifierFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.factory.IIdentifierFactory

    public final class IdentifierFactory
extends Object
implements com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.factory.IIdentifierFactory
    A factory for creating ItemIdentifiers and identifier Strings to be used in calls to the command service.

        public ItemIdentifier createItemIdentifier(String dataSourceId)

        Parameters:

        See above.

      • createItemIdentifier

                                  String dataSourceId)
        Creates and returns an ItemIdentifier with the specified key, for use in the DataSource with the specified identifier.
        Parameters:
        key - A String containing the key for this ItemIdentifier, generated using generateId().
        dataSourceId - A String containing the identifier of the DataSource, as retrieved from the info service.
        Returns:
        See above.

      • createItemIdentifierAndVersion

        public ItemIdentifierAndVersion createItemIdentifierAndVersion(String dataSourceId)
        Creates and returns an ItemIdentifierAndVersion for use in the DataSource with the specified identifier. This method generates a key for the identifier automatically, and sets the version to 1.
        Parameters:
        dataSourceId - A String containing the identifier of the DataSource, as retrieved from the info service.
        Returns:
        See above.

        key - A String containing the key for this ItemIdentifier, generated using generateId().

        version - The version of the Item that the ItemIdentifierAndVersion identifies.
        Returns:
        See above.
